  "important_notes": [
    "SqlServerConnector is @SupportsMultiTask: taskConfigs() round-robins databases across tasks via SqlServerConnection.retrieveRealDatabaseName()",
    "SqlServerConnectorConfig supports multi-database CDC via DATABASE_NAMES (comma-separated list); useSingleDatabase() returns true if list.size()==1",
    "DataQueryMode.FUNCTION uses cdc.[fn_cdc_get_all_changes_#] function; DIRECT queries change tables directly",
    "SqlServerConnection.getChangesForTable() builds a parameterized SQL query from LSN range (from/to), seqval, and operation number",
    "SqlServerOffsetContext tracks position via TxLogPosition (commitLsn + changeLsn) and eventSerialNo; Loader inner class deserializes from Kafka offset map",
    "SqlServerChangeTable stores startLsn/stopLsn bounds for change table relevance window and immutable capturedColumns list",
    "ExactlyOnceSupport.SUPPORTED declared on SqlServerConnector",
    "SnapshotIsolationMode forced to SNAPSHOT when applicationIntent=ReadOnly"
  ],

